## Basic Usage

```svelte
<script>
    import { Snap } from 'snap-ui';
</script>

<Snap.CodeTab
    npm="npm install package-name"
    yarn="yarn add package-name"
    pnpm="pnpm add package-name"
/>
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `npm` | `string` | `""` | npm command to display |
| `yarn` | `string` | `""` | yarn command to display |
| `pnpm` | `string` | `""` | pnpm command to display |
| `bun` | `string` | `""` | bun command to display |
| `defaultTab` | `string` | `"npm"` | Which tab to show by default |

